'''Ingrid Mekers''' (born 15 May 1962) is a former Belgian [[bicycle racing|racing cyclist]]. She won the [[Belgian National Road Race Championships|Belgian national road race title]] in 1983.<ref name="CyclingArchives">{{cite web |url=http://www.cyclingarchives.com/coureurfiche.php?coureurid=29394 |title=Ingrid Mekers |accessdate=3 May 2014 |work=Cycling Archives}}</ref>

